{"tid":343134,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"解決求救電話事故 OnePlus 5 又發生電池倒水問題","createTime":"2017-08-01T08:00:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T14:34:39.000Z","uid":731,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cf3910519261ac033d87eafbdde8440dde21cf53","tid":343134,"uid":731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T08:00:54.000Z","msg":"用問題天天都多去形容 OnePlus 5 可謂貼切不過，用戶無法撥打 911、112 或 999 緊急求助熱線的問題，才剛剛透過 OTA 系統更新解決不久。想不到另一波問題亦隨之而來，OnePlus 5 用戶以為解決了無法求救就能夠安枕無憂，偏偏就是系統更新令他們大為緊張。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有用戶在系統升級後，於 OnePlus 官方討論區留言投訴，表示手機出現電池倒水的問題，尤其是晚上將手機保持開機或設置了備用模式，電池仍然會流失 20% 至 50%。某些投訴的用戶都是印度電訊商 Reliance Jio 的客戶，OnePlus 回應指因為網絡訊號不佳，該電訊商的 4G LTE SIM 卡不可以用於第二 SIM 卡槽，否則會出現不斷搜尋訊號，導致電池倒水的現象。<br />\n<br />\n有趣的是， OnePlus 官方似乎未有嘗試徹底解決電池倒水問題，而是嘗試解決投訴的用戶，因為外國媒體發現他們採取刪除貼文的方法去應對。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4988/208667/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4988%2F208667%2F1%2F&d=7u%2FeXx4%2FGDu%2FYNzLwCZNftibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=c01b19ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4988/208667/1/</a>"},{"pid":"702c071dcae8f1f63bec7c95ea09b5849ee1ce6d","tid":343134,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T08:02:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3edcd9e6512506e99aced903fbf8e8e626d12c85","tid":343134,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T08:35:53.000Z","msg":"oneplus已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5ab2cbc004a0ab8860a175ce72b0491f732175d","tid":343134,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T10:14:33.000Z","msg":"咇咧叭喇<br />\n咇咧叭喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4836eb4a252f6a9ab2e321479d1ede9031ab8512","tid":343134,"uid":63,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":